    <div class="container-fluid" style="margin-top:50px"></div>

    <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto p-5 py-5">
    <h1>🔧DevPage</h1>
        <button class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-sm btn-start" type="button">컨트랙트 시작 </button>
    <div class ="pt-3 my-4 border-top">
        <h4>크라우드 펀딩 컨트랙트로 생성한 토큰 보내기</h4>
        크라우드 펀딩 컨트랙트 주소: <input type="text" id="_address_to" size="20"/>
         <br/>
        보낼 토큰 개수: <input type="text" id="_how_many" size="20"/><br/>
        <button class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-sm btn-token" type="button">Send</button>
        <br/>
    </div>
    <div class ="pt-3 my-4 border-top">
        <h4>크라우드 펀딩 컨트랙트 함수</h4>
        <button class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-sm btn-checkGoal" type="button">checkGoal</button>
		기간끝나면 목표달성했는지 확인<br />
        <button class ="btn btn-outline-dark btn-sm btn-sendEther" type ="button">sendEther</button>
		목표달성 성공시 입금 / 목표달성 실패시 환불
    </div>
    <div class ="pt-3 my-4 border-top">
        <h4>크라우드 펀딩 컨트랙트 정보 확인</h4>
        <div class="input-group mb-1">
            <button class ="btn btn-outline-dark btn-sm btn-amountCheck" type ="button">현재 청약 금액</button>
            <input disabled class="form-control" type = "text" id = "amountRaised">
        </div>
        <div class="input-group mb-1">
            <button class ="btn btn-sm btn-outline-dark btn-beneficiary" type ="button">식당 주인 주소</button>
            <input disabled class="form-control" type = "text" id = "beneficiary">
        </div>
        <div class="input-group mb-1">
            <button class ="btn btn-sm btn-outline-dark btn-crowdsaleClosed" type ="button">펀딩 마감</button>
            <input disabled class="form-control" type = "text" id = "crowdsaleClosed">
        </div>
        <div class="input-group mb-1">
            <button class ="btn btn-sm btn-outline-dark btn-deadline" type ="button">마감 기한</button>
            <input disabled class="form-control" type = "text" id = "deadline">
        </div>
        <div class="input-group mb-1">
            <button class ="btn btn-sm btn-outline-dark btn-fundingGoal" type ="button">펀딩 목표 금액</button>
            <input disabled class="form-control" type = "text" id = "fundingGoal">
        </div>
        <div class="input-group mb-1">
            <button class ="btn btn-sm btn-outline-dark btn-fundingGoalReached" type ="button">목표 달성 여부</button>
            <input disabled class="form-control" type = "text" id = "fundingGoalReached">
        </div>
        <div class="input-group mb-1">
            <button class ="btn btn-sm btn-outline-dark btn-price" type ="button">가격</button>
            <input disabled class="form-control" type = "text" id = "price">
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
